-- PepsiCo reaffirms 2007 earnings forecast
-- 
-- Thu Feb 22, 2007 12:51pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/02/22/us-pepsico-results-idUSWEN464820070222

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - PepsiCo Inc. reaffirmed on Thursday its 2007 earnings forecast of at least $3.30 per share. 


 The company also said it still expects mid-single digit growth in net revenue and volume, according to a filing with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission. Analysts, on average, expect PepsiCo to post 2007 earnings of $3.32 a share, according to Reuters Estimates.